data.description: PRICE REDUCED!! Welcome home to this 4 bedroom MOVE-IN READY home, situated on a large corner lot in the heart of Spring Hill. This home has beautiful wood plank tiles located throughout the home. The spacious open floor plan is perfect for entertaining your family and friends. The kitchen has been updated with Granite countertops, white shaker cabinets, subway tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and has a large beautiful center island. The guest bathroom has a spa like feel with wood plank tiles up the walls. The master bedroom is very spacious and private. You can use the back bedroom as a large bedroom or as a bonus room! The backyard is fully fenced in and private.  Located close to shopping, restaurants, medical facilities, Weeki Wachee Springs, and the Suncoast Parkway for a quick commute to Tampa. Don't miss out, call today to schedule your showing. One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged
